OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,FManchester Airport has been ranked the
OL,7,Fworst in the UK for flight delays,
OL,8,Fwith Liverpool John Lennon Airport
OL,9,Fhaving the most punctual flights.
OL,11,FDepartures from Manchester, that is
OL,12,Fthe country's third busiest airport
OL,13,Fwere an average of 19.5 minutes behind
OL,14,Fschedule in 2025, according to
OL,15,Fanalysis of Civil Aviation Authority
OL,16,F(CAA) data
OL,18,FThat was longer than all other UK
OL,19,Fairports despite representing a 30
OL,20,Fsecond improvement from the previous
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
