CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,FFlight delays are often caused by
OL,7,Fissues outside the control of
OL,8,Fairports, such as air traffic control
OL,9,F(ATC) disruption and bad weather.
OL,11,FRory Boland, editor of magazine Which?
OL,12,FTravel, said the choice of airport
OL,13,F"shouldn't make or break your trip"
OL,14,Fbut "too many holidays got off to a
OL,15,Fterrible start last year".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@cO]vD@EOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
