PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,FHe said: "Manchester Airport has
OL,7,Franked last in our airport survey for
OL,8,Ffour consecutive years and these new
OL,9,FCAA figures validate why this is a
OL,10,Fparticularly poor place to be stranded
OL,11,Fduring delays."
OL,13,FBirmingham Airport had the second
OL,14,Fpoorest flight punctuality last year,
OL,15,Fwith an average delay of 18 minutes
OL,16,Fand 42 seconds.
OL,18,FIn third place was Bournemouth Airport
OL,19,F(17 minutes and 18 seconds).
OL,26,@nD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
