OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,FLiverpool John Lennon Airport recorded
OL,7,Fan average delay of just nine minutes
OL,8,Fand 24 seconds.
OL,10,FThe analysis took into account
OL,11,Fscheduled and chartered departures
OL,12,Ffrom the 23 commercial UK airports
OL,13,Fwith at least 1,000 outbound flights
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FCancellations were not included. The
OL,17,Faverage delay for departures last year
OL,18,Fwas 14 minutes and 54 seconds, down
OL,19,Ffrom 18 minutes and 24 seconds in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
