PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,FManchester and Heathrow are the two UK
OL,7,Fairports with two-runways. Manchester
OL,8,FAirport was used by 32 million
OL,9,Fpassengers last year.
OL,11,FIts scheme to revamp Terminal 3 is
OL,12,Fongoing, while a 10-year #1.3 billion
OL,13,Ftransformation which included
OL,14,Fmodernising and doubling the size of
OL,15,FTerminal 2, and closing Terminal 1,
OL,16,Fwas recently completed.
OL,18,FA spokesperson for Manchester Airport
OL,19,Fsaid: "Punctuality is affected by
OL,20,Ffactors that are outside of an
OL,21,Fairport's control."
OL,26,@{D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
