OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,F"The two most significant factors
OL,7,Fcontributing to delays in the last
OL,8,Fyear have been industrial action
OL,9,Faffecting air traffic control in
OL,10,FEurope, and the weather."
OL,12,F"These were exacerbated by airspace
OL,13,Frestrictions above conflict zones
OL,14,Fmeaning airports with significant long-
OL,15,Fhaul networks, like Manchester, were
OL,16,Fmore significantly affected than
OL,17,Fothers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
