PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,F"As an industry we are working
OL,7,Fcollectively to achieve the best
OL,8,Fpossible on-time departure rates,
OL,9,Fwhile protecting flight schedules and
OL,10,Favoiding the need for cancellations."
OL,12,FDepending on the distance of the route
OL,13,Fand length of delay, passengers booked
OL,14,Fon delayed flights from UK airports
OL,15,Fare entitled to assistance such as a
OL,16,Freasonable amount of food and drink, a
OL,17,Fmeans to communicate and overnight
OL,18,Faccommodation if required.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
