PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777997460
OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,FAnna Bowles, head of consumer at the
OL,7,FCAA, urged the aviation industry to be
OL,8,F"focused on delivering punctual and
OL,9,Freliable journeys for passengers
OL,10,Fwherever possible" as she warned that
OL,11,Fdelays have a "real impact for people
OL,12,Fheading off on holidays".
OL,14,FShe added: "When disruption occurs,
OL,15,Fhow the industry responds really
OL,16,Fmatters."Passengers should be kept
OL,17,Finformed and given the care and
OL,18,Fsupport they are entitled to."
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@RO]sD@OOUtD@XO]vD@LOUxD@IOUzD@
