OL,3,CNorth West Airports are best and worst
OL,4,Cfor flight delays
OL,6,FA spokesperson for trade body
OL,7,FAirportsUK said passengers are
OL,8,F"benefitting from improvements in the
OL,9,Fservice they receive", and delays in
OL,10,F2025 were "down significantly on the
OL,11,Fprevious year".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@UO]rD@KOUsD@NO]
